The paper deals with image manipulation and generation, specifically reshaping objects in images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The proposed ReshapeGAN architecture is a deep learning model, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also mentions testing on multiple datasets, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) category.
